git show ff1632ae27c4198b71cf09d9b80d55a652d3b9fb

There were 2 logging problems reproducible with a large number of ELBs. The logging in DnsServerHandler is due to queries that arrive before the services are fully enabled. The error logging in ErrorHandlerSupport makes the logs unusable. The root cause of the error logging is that the context is not found because the service clients are closed due to timeout.

{noformat}
 com.eucalyptus.context.NoSuchContextException: Found correlation id 36d99f04-254b-4b1a-a325-68c9c0104785 but no corresponding context. 
{noformat}
